Package fr.ign.artiscales.pm.analysis

Class GetParametersOfScene

java.lang.Object
fr.ign.artiscales.pm.analysis.GetParametersOfScene
public class GetParametersOfScene
extends java.lang.Object
This class generates values for the description of an urban fabric. It is aimed to help the setting of ProfileUrbanFabric parameters. It can work on different scales, from the block or the zonePreciseNameField of a zoning plan to a whole community.
